我需要你对下面这个Java代码进行调整，要求要解决两个问题
1、Return value of java.util.concurrent.CountDownLatch.await(long, TimeUnit) ignored in com.huawei.fiber.service.impl.QuerySegmentsServiceImpl.getCircuitInfos(String[])
2、非SpringIOC纳管的对象不能存在成员变量线程池，防止对象创建时，线程不可控

```
public class QuerySegmentsServiceImpl implements IQuerySegmentsService {

    private static final Logger LOGGER = LoggerFactory.getLogger(QuerySegmentsServiceImpl.class);

    private final CountDownLatch latch;

    public QuerySegmentsServiceImpl(int circuitLength) {
        latch = new CountDownLatch(circuitLength);
    }

    ThreadPoolExecutor threadPoolExecutor = new ThreadPoolExecutor(100, 500, 10, TimeUnit.SECONDS, new LinkedBlockingDeque<>(10000));

    @Override
    public List<JSONObject> getCircuitInfos(String[] circuitInfos) {
        // 数组判空
        if (circuitInfos == null || circuitInfos.length <= 0) {
            return new ArrayList<>();
        }

        List<JSONObject> circuitInfoList = Collections.synchronizedList(new ArrayList<>());
        for (int i = 0; i < circuitInfos.length; i++) {

            if (!StringUtils.isEmpty(circuitInfos[i])) {
                String circuitInfo = circuitInfos[i];
                threadPoolExecutor.submit(new Thread(() -> getCircuitInfo(circuitInfo, circuitInfoList), circuitInfo));
            }
        }
        try {
            latch.await(60,TimeUnit.SECONDS);
        } catch (InterruptedException e) {
            LOGGER.error("query optical circuit link segments interruptedException.");
        }
        threadPoolExecutor.shutdown();
        return circuitInfoList;
    }

    public List<JSONObject> getCircuitInfo(String circuitInfo, List<JSONObject> circuitInfoList) {
        // call app service
        try {
            JSONObject segmentJson = ServiceUtil.getSegmentList(circuitInfo);
            circuitInfoList.add(segmentJson);
            return circuitInfoList;
        } finally {
            latch.countDown();
        }
    }
}
```
